av saksøkte Loewen-gruppen.

1977
01:54:07,916 --> 01:54:09,625
Du fortjener det. Kom an!

1978
01:55:07,166 --> 01:55:09,083
500 millioner dollar, Jerry.

1979
01:55:12,208 --> 01:55:13,500
Jeg vet det, Willie.

1980
01:55:16,541 --> 01:55:17,625
Jeg vet det.

1981
01:55:49,375 --> 01:55:50,791
Hei, Willie.

1982
01:55:52,666 --> 01:55:53,833
Hei, Mame.

1983
01:55:54,375 --> 01:55:57,708
Hva gjør du? Er du her for å få mer bank?

1984
01:55:57,958 --> 01:56:00,458
Mer bank? Nei.

1985
01:56:00,458 --> 01:56:03,333
- Jeg ville faktisk bare gratulere deg.
- Å ja?

1986
01:56:03,333 --> 01:56:05,166
- Ja.
- Gratulere meg?

1987
01:56:06,166 --> 01:56:08,083
Mener du det?

1988
01:56:09,291 --> 01:56:10,708
Jeg hater å tape,

1989
01:56:10,708 --> 01:56:13,416
